
combine
 *70 g flour 
 *12 g  sugar
 *1/4 tsp baking powder
whisk has in a large bowl 
 *1 egg
 *14 g oil or melted butter 
 whisk in
  *150 g milk
whisk in dry ingredients
let rest 10 minutes

for each crepe

heat skillet on medium-high to 450
lightly oil with paper towel
add 1/3 cup of batter
spread with a spoon 
cook until top  appears dry
flip
cook 15 seconds


yields 4 crepes 

garnish each with
30-50 g ham
15-30 g cheese
béchamel 
mushrooms 

or

fruits
40g melted chocolate 

